definitions.definition: A male given name from the Germanic languages .
A surname originating as a patronymic .

subdefinitions.definition: A community in New Tecumseth , Simcoe County , Canada .

A number of places in the United States : Former name of White Hall , California . A former town in Helt Township, Vermillion County , Indiana . A minor city in Hamilton County , Iowa . A minor city in Jewell County , Kansas . A minor city in Morrison County , Minnesota . An unincorporated community in Monongalia County , West Virginia . A town in Kenosha County , Wisconsin . An unincorporated community in Anderson , Burnett County , Wisconsin .
